asset.hookText: The third PB&RJ tour stop of 2007 went down at Northern California's Sierra-At-Tahoe resort Saturday January 6th, 2007. The custom PBRJ setup consisted of a 30ft double barrel, a large battleship and a daunting device dubbed the "swing set". Music by Riverboat Gamblers.
